Elliott Whitehead (born 4 September 1989) is an English professional rugby league footballer who plays as a second-row forward for the Canberra Raiders in the NRL, and England and Great Britain at international level. 
He previously played for the Bradford Bulls and the Catalans Dragons in the Super League.
